data.description: Your Dream Home Awaits! Step into a world of comfort and style with this Fantastic three-bedroom, two-bathroom home that's sure to steal your heart! With a multitude of upgrades, this property is a true gem. The Remodeled Kitchen is sure to delight. Many upgrades include: Custom paint, upgraded flooring, mature & lush vegetation and a fully fenced yard. The backyard features a water feature and covered patio that is perfect for outdoor relaxation. There is a bonus family room giving you added space for entertaining guests and family. This home isn't just a house; it's a sanctuary. Imagine evenings under your covered patio, entertaining friends and family, and enjoying the serenity of mature trees surrounding your oasis. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise. Your search is over! Be sure to schedule a viewing and make this dream home yours!
